*Delta Modulation :

Analog Signal ---==> Comparator -------------------------------> Digital Data
                ||                                      |
                ||-------------------------------------||
                ||-- Delay Unit <--- Starecase Maker <==|

/* DELTA MODULATOR */

Digital Signal ---==> Starecase Maker ---> Low-pass filter ---> Analog Data
                 |                   |
                 |--- Delay Unit <---|

/* DELTA DEMODULATOR */

