Line Coding Scheme
                 V
                 |---> Unipolar ---> Non-Return-to-Zero
                 |
                 |---> Polar ----|---> Non-Return-to-Zero-Level
                 |               |---> Non-Return-to-Zero-Invert
                 |               |---> Biphase ---> Manchester
                 |                        |---> Differential Manchester
                 |
                 |---> Bipolar --|---> AMI
                                 |---> Pseudoternary

